	DESC:You responded to the mobs of Galtan citizens with nonviolence, and in so doing helped forge a path for a peaceful resolution to what could have become an international incident. For your actions, you receive official commendation from the government of Andoran. All of your characters gain access to the Oath of the People's Council (Pathfinder Player Companion: Divine Anthology 20) as if it appeared on the Additional Resources list. Include a copy of this Chronicle sheet with the records of any PC who selects this option.

